<br>
One of the things I do against healer/casters is to switch to fast one handed weapons, this does two things:<br>
<br>
1) More hits in the same amount of time allows for a greater likelihood of the DOT proc to fire off and inflict greater damage.<br>
<br>
2) Keeps them interrupted so they cannot get off a spell other than a instant.<br>
<br>
Not the best tactic but it does work. <p>Berdoon 50Skald Igraine 6xx Weapons Smith<br>
