<br>
I try to choose primary targets that will benefit my group, if I am interrupting the healer or caster,  less heals are getting to my opponent and/or less damage to my group.  I just try to study what is the best target for me, I can assist the main tanks or keep the casters/healers in fits, it all depends on the group I am with.  I follow the philosophy of knowing your targets and where you benefit the group most.<br>
<br>
As far as the DOT proc, if I am swinging a weapon that lands 2.2 times more often than the 2h, I am just as likely or more likely to land a DOT of the same strength as the one on the 2her.  I don't think Mythic would code it as such that the 2h weapons are twice as likely as the 1h weapons to land the DOT.  <br>
